arrive(string,string,uint256).notice: Sets a location in the locations array when the package arrives    at a new location. Also publicly alerts via `Arrived`.

deliver(string,string,uint256).notice: Sets a location in the locations array when the package arrives    at the final destination. Also publicly alerts via `Arrived` and    `Delivered`.

depart(uint256,uint256).notice: Sets the departure time of the location in the locations array. Also    publicly alerts via `Departed`.

getDetails().notice: Gets all the details for the package contract in 1 call.

getLocations().notice: Gets all the locations in the array.
